data.description: Great space on Preibe Lake just blocks away from White Bear Lake.  This home has the potential to be an absolute gem!   3 bedrooms on one level and a fourth in the lower level with its own bathroom. The possibilities are endless with this home! Enjoy  your summers canoeing on the lake or grilling on the deck. The lake is also a perfect place to practice your ice skating skills in the winter! Do you have a dog? There is also a fully fenced back yard! Come take a look!
